OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,6,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,8,Ffurther showers for a time in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny scattered showers will
OL,12,Fclear this evening. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will then be dry with clear
OL,14,Fspells, though some mist and fog may
OL,15,Faffect northern coastal areas.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FDry and settled with light
OL,18,Fwinds. Fairly cloudy at first, but
OL,19,Fbrightening up with some good spells
OL,20,Fof warm sunshine for the rest of the
OL,21,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
